        "javadoc": "/**\n * Returns {@code true} if {@code value} represents a real number. This is\n * equivalent to, but not necessarily implemented as,\n * {@code !(Float.isInfinite(value) || Float.isNaN(value))}.\n *\n * @since 10.0\n */\n",
